Audio.Title: Aa gaya mere hothon pe naam-e-nabi
Hashr Mein Kuch Mile Na Mile
Mainu Yaar Di Namaaz Pad Lain Dey
Ya Mere Data Waliyan De Raja
Ali Ali Ali Maula Ali Ali
Is Karam Ka Karon  Shukar Kaise
Gham hai ya khushi hai tun
Na swal ban ke mila karo
Sohne Mukhre Da Lain De Nazaara
Ni Main Jaana Jogi De Naal
Sanu Ek Pal Chain Na Aawe
Sun Charkhe Di Mithi Mithi Ghook
Jis Dil wich Sajna Was Jayiye
Dil Marjaane Nu Ki Hoya Sajna
Eh Sochan Soch Ke Dil Mera
Gal Kar Koi Peen Pilavan Di
Ho Jaave Je Pyar Te Sona
Haje Latha Nahio Akhiyan Da Cha
Rabba Kadi Wi Na Pain Vichhore
Je Kadey Mera Yaar Mil Jaye
Mainu Yaar Di Namaaz Padh Lain De
Bewafa Se Bhi Pyar Hota Hai
Yeh Jo Halka Halka Suroor Hai
Gham Hai Ya Khushi Hai Tu
Dil Sulagta Raha Chandni Raat Mein
Haqeeqat Ka Agar Afsana Ban Jaye
Ab Dekh Ke Jee Ghabrata Hai
Main Khayal Hun Kisi Aur Ka
Sanson Ki Maala Pe Simrun Main
Hai Kahan Ka Irada Tumhara Sanam
Gale Lipte Hain Woh Bijli Ke Dar Se
Puchha Kisi Ne Haal Kisi Ka
Tumne Bhi Thukra Hi Diya Hai
Na Sawal Ban Ke Mila Karo
Is Karam Ka Karun Shukar Kaise
Aewain Bol Na Banere Utte Kaawa
Tasbi De Ik Ik Daane Te
